# Visual-storyboard frames: regenerable review artifacts (tst_visual.qml /
# tools/uidriver.cpp), written for human eyeballing, never read by tests.
# The canonical output location is build/screenshots; these entries cover
# runs that wrote into the source tree instead. screenshots/press/ is the
# exception: curated, committed capture assets referenced by the README
# and the AppStream metadata.
/screenshots/*
!/screenshots/press/
/tests/screenshots/
# Packaging outputs
dist/
packaging/linux/.tools/
